%% 3.1.6 Vehicle Management — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database
%% Driver dropdown: GET User/Search với role driver | Tạo xe: POST Bus/Create (chưa gắn driver trong Bus entity — gán lái qua BusAssignment + lịch nếu có).

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (/vehicles)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant BC as Controller (BusController)
    participant BS as Service (BusService)
    participant Repo as Repository (Bus User)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Vehicle Management
    UI->>BC: GET /api/Bus/Search (grid)
    BC->>BS: SearchBusAsync
    BS->>Repo: Query buses
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    BS-->>BC: paged
    BC-->>UI: 200 — Status, Capacity, ...

    Note over UI,US: Load driver dropdown (filter by name)
    UI->>UC: GET /api/User/Search?role=driver&...
    UC->>US: SearchUserAsync
    US->>Repo: Query users role driver
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    US-->>UC: driver list
    UC-->>UI: 200 — pick e.g. Mr. Nguyen Van A

    Actor->>UI: Plate, Capacity, select driver, Submit

    alt Capacity invalid e.g. -1 (frontend only)
        UI->>UI: Red border — block submit
    else Valid
        UI->>BC: POST /api/Bus/Create BusCreateDto
        BC->>BS: CreateBusAsync(dto)
        BS->>BS: ValidateCapacity greater than 0 (server)
        BS->>Repo: Add Bus + SaveChanges
        Repo->>DB: INSERT
        DB-->>Repo: OK
        BS-->>BC: success message
        BC-->>UI: 200 Bus created successfully
        UI-->>Actor: Toast / refresh grid
    end

    Note over Actor,DB: BR06 — chặn mua package khi bus full: kiểm tra ở Order/Package service khi available seats = 0.
